k \in \mathbb{N}
\sqrt{k\pi} < \xi_k < \sqrt{(k+1)\pi}
\int_{\sqrt{k\pi}}^{\sqrt{(k+1)\pi}} \sin(x^2) \, dx = \frac{(-1)^k}{\xi_k}
